    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/f56e30edae0822d6e128068c9ccb20b3.avif?t=1616164459\" width=616 height=134 /></span><br><br>宁静村庄的祥和气氛突然被打破，被诅咒的史莱姆大量入侵，手持弓箭的少女和她的奶奶，必须依靠自己的力量拯救村庄……隐藏在史莱姆、致命陷阱和神秘道具之后的究竟是什么样的秘密？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/3acb4b2e6e67564b7955c93fcf5a59c1.webp?t=1616164459\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/f5d0a943583b3422679c693ad809cb45.poster.avif?t=1616164459\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/f5d0a943583b3422679c693ad809cb45.webm?t=1616164459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>汲取了诸多前辈游戏的养分，经过不断的调整优化，《黑水绮谭》带来了独特的游戏性和画面。在快节奏的体验和适当的难度中进行平衡，游戏提供了46个设计精巧的关卡，三种不同的游戏难度，让游戏既有动作游戏的爽快感，又不失挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/0460c869e75212ae7a6fb90b1e6de36e.webp?t=1616164459\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>利用一把弓箭，实现普通攻击、爆炸攻击以及子弹时间等等技巧。在击败入侵的史莱姆的同时，还需要依靠灵活机动的操作躲开致命的陷阱。十几种不同的技能组合，将带来各自不同的乐趣。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/3d2ada89b1c1279891cf124dc1c07555.poster.avif?t=1616164459\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/3d2ada89b1c1279891cf124dc1c07555.webm?t=1616164459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>随着游戏的深入，弓箭少女将拥有白发模式，在该模式之下，她将拥有瞬移技巧，大大提升了游戏的操作感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/82f39ee801c02047cca6db59cceb14d3.poster.avif?t=1616164459\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/82f39ee801c02047cca6db59cceb14d3.webm?t=1616164459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>而在特定的时候，玩家还可以操作奶奶角色，这又是一种完全不同的体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/f298c5679a0fc8a2b5be75f750888e89.poster.avif?t=1616164459\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/f298c5679a0fc8a2b5be75f750888e89.webm?t=1616164459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1235830/extras/eac16504e03211f069f8b017663d65be.webp?t=1616164459\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><br>丰富的色彩和明快的风格，让人耳目一新。无论是人物风格设计、环境、甚至是水体的表现，都展现了《黑水绮谭》在美术上的用心。<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><i><strong>《黑水绮谭》推荐各位玩家使用手柄操作</strong></i></li></ul>",
